skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my diary
des: Simply say something like "ask my diary what to write", Alexa will prompt you with a suggestion. If you don't like the suggestion, say "next" then Alexa will give you another one.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
